title: Foreign Policy
new-page: true
is-card: true
tags: potus_affairs, cabinet
on-arrival: {!
    Q.month_actions += 1;
    Q.foreign_policy_timer += 8;
    if (Q.french_mexico < 2 && Q.year >= 1868) {
        Q.french_mexico = 2;
    }
!}
view-if: sect_state_party = "R" and foreign_policy_timer <= 0
card-image: img/portraits/Seward.jpg
go-to: fp_menu

= Foreign Policy

What should our foreign policy priority be?

@fp_menu

- @pressure_mexico
- @pressure_mexico2
